1 such a hearing shall be granted as soon as is practicable and convenient
2 for all persons concerned. The request for such a hearing shall be made
3 in writing by the employee alleging the grievance and shall be directed
4 to the executive director. After hearing all testimony surrounding the
5 grievance of such employee, the brand committee, at its discretion, may
6 approve, rescind, nullify, or amend all actions as previously taken by
7 the executive director.
