1 Sec. 25. Sections 11 and 26 of this act become operative on January
2 1, 2027. The other sections of this act become operative on their
3 effective date.
4 Sec. 26. Original section 54-192, Reissue Revised Statutes of
5 Nebraska, is repealed.
6 Sec. 27. Original sections 54-170, 54-171, 54-189, 54-191,
7 54-1,102, 54-1,108, 54-1,111, 54-1,116, 54-1,120, and 54-1,122, Reissue
